### Project Objective
Construct a dynamic, factor‑based equity portfolio on the entire US stock universe (or a very large subset) and rigorously evaluate its out‑of‑sample performance against standard benchmarks. You will ingest and clean massive tick‑level data, estimate rolling multi‑factor models, solve constrained portfolio optimizations, implement a realistic backtest, and produce a comprehensive risk‑attribution report.

